original_title: Pinkalicious & Peterrific: Cupid Calls It Quits
overview: It’s Valentine’s Day in Pinkville, and Pinkalicious can’t wait! When Pinkalicious and Peter befriend the Cupid, he offers them a trade: he’ll become a real kid and join Pinkalicious’s class, while Pinkalicious is Cupid for the day!
tagline: It’s Valentine’s Day in Pinkville, and Pinkalicious can’t wait!
title: Pinkalicious & Peterrific: Cupid Calls It Quits
